@startuml
title PCI HSM Life-Cycle Chain of Trust (Modules L and M)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #FDEEEE
skinparam activityBorderColor #B54A4A
skinparam activityDiamondBackgroundColor #FCF5F5
skinparam activityDiamondBorderColor #B54A4A
skinparam ArrowColor #B54A4A

start
:Design & certification\n(change control, L1);
:Firmware inspected, free of\nhidden functions (L2);
:Assembly with certified\nhardware, dual control (L4/L5);
:Install unique device secret\nunder dual control (L7);
if (Tamper-evident package\nor self-erasing secret?) then (yes)
  :Ship under auditable controls (M1/M3);
else (no)
  :Account for every device\nat every point in time (M1);
endif
:Transfer accountability to\nnext party (M2);
if (Authenticity of device\nverified at deployment?) then (yes)
  :Initial key loading\nby acquiring org (M5/M6);
else (no)
  :Reject device;
  stop
endif
:Operational use\n(out of PCI HSM scope);
stop
@enduml
